    - rid: 4289126188471549965
      type: {class: LocalizedTextToSpeechMetadata, ns: NMY.GoogleCloudTextToSpeech, asm: com.nmy.googlecloudtexttospeech}
      data:
        created: 2024-02-26 16:44:33
        lastModified: 2024-02-26 16:44:33
        spokenText: Gut, jetzt beginnt der Chirurg, Instrumente anzufordern
    - rid: 4289126188471549967
      type: {class: LocalizedTextToSpeechMetadata, ns: NMY.GoogleCloudTextToSpeech, asm: com.nmy.googlecloudtexttospeech}
      data:
        created: 2024-02-26 16:44:33
        lastModified: 2024-02-26 16:44:33
        spokenText: Nimm dir ein beliebiges Instrument, um zu lernen, wie man es
          korrekt anreicht
    - rid: 4289126188471549969
      type: {class: LocalizedTextToSpeechMetadata, ns: NMY.GoogleCloudTextToSpeech, asm: com.nmy.googlecloudtexttospeech}
      data:
        created: 2024-02-26 16:44:34
        lastModified: 2024-02-26 16:44:34
        spokenText: 'Reminder: Hebe einen beliebigen Gegenstand auf'
    - rid: 4289126188471549971
      type: {class: LocalizedTextToSpeechMetadata, ns: NMY.GoogleCloudTextToSpeech, asm: com.nmy.googlecloudtexttospeech}
      data:
        created: 2024-02-26 16:44:34
        lastModified: 2024-03-04 10:40:41
        spokenText: Halte das Instrument jetzt direkt in die Kamera, um es zu scannen.
    - rid: 4289126188471549973
      type: {class: LocalizedTextToSpeechMetadata, ns: NMY.GoogleCloudTextToSpeech, asm: com.nmy.googlecloudtexttospeech}
      data:
